WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy C1-M08: Stories, literature and creative expression. Learners practise edit for precision through narratives, characters, plot, poetry, performance. The teacher models cohesion and paragraph flow, introduces vocabulary such as genres, characters, settings, plot, figurative language, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
